{"id":239249,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/维权网-北京丰台被强拆村民多人被拘留/","date":"2012-07-11T14:16:09Z","modified":"2012-07-11T14:16:09Z","title":"维权网 | 北京丰台被强拆村民多人被拘留","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'> </a>（维权网信息员张成报道）7<span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日中午</span><span>，北京丰台区南苑乡石榴庄村村民黄玉卿、宋振明、李焕君、徐慧贞、张宗钢、姜流勇、黎建波、焦建秋、郭志英、孙双燕等人，因自己房屋于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日</span><span>被村委会组织人员非法强拆，无家可归，到天安门金水桥边向毛泽东像磕头，随即被警察扣压。</span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>日</span><span>，家属获得消息，除孙双燕在派出所喝农药自杀正在医院抢救，徐慧贞因血压</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">180</span><span>被丰台看守所拒收外，其他</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>人全部被行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>天，理由是扰乱公共秩序。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>村民姜流勇的家人表示，不知道拘留应不应该给家属下书面通知单，我只收到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>号晚的一个电话，说有可能被拘留，之后就什么消息也没有了。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>相关详情请参见：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2012/07/blog-post_2244.html\">http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2012/07/blog-post_2244.html</a></span></div>\n<p></span></div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-7881803612967739227?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_p